name: open me for instructions
info:
This flow only supports modules connected via TCP, not rs485.

NODE read_val function: set unit number to match dingtian module number for each module. (1, 2 or 3)

NODE relay_status (bin): set the appropriate ip address for each module. Select type:TCP and TCP type:TELNET. leave unit ID at 1.

For each module being read, enable the appropriate number of relay nodes, and set the relay numbers accordingly. (example: Two units with 4 relays each you would enable 4 relays for unit one, numbers 3-6. Enable 4 relays for unit two, 7-10.)
